query:
UPDATE energy_bill_uploads
            SET
                bill_period_start = $2,
                bill_period_end = $3,
                total_kwh_encrypted = $4,
                energy_type = $5,
                provider = $6,
                postal_code = $7,
                file_hash = $8,
                file_path_encrypted = $9,
                ocr_confidence = $10,
                manually_verified = $11,
                verified_at = $12,
                verified_by = $13,
                consent_timestamp = $14,
                consent_ip = $15,
                consent_user_agent = $16,
                consent_signature_hash = $17,
                anonymized = $18,
                retention_until = $19,
                deleted_at = $20,
                updated_at = $21
            WHERE id = $1
